<table width=70%>
<tr><td>Mana:</td>
<td>0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Skill:</td>
<td>Evocation</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>Items:</td>
<td>
<a href="/weapons/piercing.shtml#drogan_obsidian_dagger">Drogan Obsidian Dagger</a><br>
<a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml#obsidian_flamberge">Obsidian Flamberge</a><br>
<a href="/weapons/piercing.shtml#obsidian_shard">Obsidian Shard</a><br>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>Buyable:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Researchable:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Drops from MOB:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Cast Time:</td>
<td>0.00 seconds</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><br></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>Description:</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
Reduces target's AC by 6 and deals 30 damage to target.</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
<BR>1 tick = 6 seconds<BR>
When a range of effects are given, it usually means that the effect becomes more potent as the caster increases in levels.
